<p>From the extract, we can quickly note that Bajaj Auto sells around 2M vehicles in the global market.</p>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><em><strong>How many units of two-wheelers and CVs does Bajaj Auto sell in India and the International market?</strong></em></span></p>
<p>Now that we have established that Bajaj has a domestic and international market, it makes sense to figure out how many units of bikes and commercial vehicles are sold in India and in the International market.</p>
