<p>Let us continue our QnA.</p>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><em><strong>How much revenue do they make?</strong></em></span></p>
<p>The most crucial question perhaps ðŸ˜Š</p>
<p>Clearly, when we talk about revenue for this company, we need to figure four essential things â€“</p>
