<p>But here is where the challenge occurs; the company does not easily give out this information. The information we have is â€“</p>
<p><a href="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Image-7_rev.png"><img alt="" class="aligncenter wp-image-10083" height="105" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" src="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Image-7_rev-300x63.png" srcset="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Image-7_rev-300x63.png 300w, https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Image-7_rev-768x161.png 768w, https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Image-7_rev.png 890w" width="500"/></a></p>
